SELECT DISTINCT V1.AUTHOR_ID AS ID FROM VIEWS V1, VIEWS V2 WHERE V1.AUTHOR_ID=V2.VIEWER_ID AND V1.ARTICLE_ID=V2.ARTICLE_ID ORDER BY V1.AUTHOR_ID
SELECT DISTINCT AUTHOR_ID AS ID FROM VIEWS S WHERE AUTHOR_ID = VIEWER_ID ORDER BY AUTHOR_ID
SELECT AUTHOR_ID AS ID FROM VIEWS WHERE AUTHOR_ID = VIEWER_ID GROUP BY ID ORDER BY AUTHOR_ID
SELECT DISTINCT(V1.AUTHOR_ID) AS ID FROM VIEWS V1, VIEWS V2 WHERE V1.AUTHOR_ID = V2.VIEWER_ID AND V1.VIEWER_ID = V2.VIEWER_ID ORDER BY ID
SELECT DISTINCT A.AUTHOR_ID AS ID FROM VIEWS A JOIN VIEWS B USING (AUTHOR_ID) WHERE A.AUTHOR_ID = B.VIEWER_ID ORDER BY ID
SELECT AUTHOR_ID AS ID FROM VIEWS V WHERE V.AUTHOR_ID=V.VIEWER_ID GROUP BY ID ORDER BY ID
SELECT DISTINCT VIEWER_ID AS ID FROM VIEWS WHERE AUTHOR_ID = VIEWER_ID ORDER BY 1 ASC
SELECT AUTHOR_ID AS ID FROM VIEWS WHERE AUTHOR_ID= VIEWER_ID GROUP BY AUTHOR_ID,VIEWER_ID ORDER BY AUTHOR_ID
SELECT AUTHOR_ID ID FROM VIEWS WHERE AUTHOR_ID = VIEWER_ID GROUP BY 1 ORDER BY 1
